column2: SELECT z.allamID, z.ra1, z.dec1, z.ra2, z.dec2, z.allam_redshift1, z.allam_redshift2, z.SpecObjID as SpecObjID_dr7, z.mjd as mjd_dr7, z.plate as plate_dr7, z.fiberID as fiberID_dr7, z.z as z_dr7, p.objID as objID_dr1#, s.bestObjID as bestObjID as bestObjID_dr1#, s.SpecObjID as SpecObjID_dr1#, s.mjd as mjd_dr1#, s.plate as plate_dr1#, s.fiberID as fiberID_dr1#, s.z as z_dr1# into mydb.test FROM dr1#.PhotoObjAll as p JOIN dr1#.SpecObjAll as s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID and s.specObjID = p.specObjID JOIN mydb.zPairs as z ON z.mjd = s.mjd WHERE s.plate = z.plate AND s.fiberID = z.fiberID ORDER BY z.allamID
